Meet <b>Desiree</b>, our Citizen of the Week!<br><br>This Metro Park resident is a total animal lover. Her home at <a href='/home/?user=nadatall'>9276-A Timberwolf Way</a> boasts an array of pets that get pampered and petted every day. Since May 13, 2006, Desiree has decorated her home in a beautiful style to please people and animals alike!<br><br>Desiree does not shy away from color when it comes to decorating. Violet and green, two of her favorite shades, are well-represented. And it shouldn't come as a surprise that she enjoys collecting everything zebra-patterned in Millsberry. If the <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=9">Pet Palace</a> sold zebras, Desiree would definitely have one. <br><br>She has great compassion for her furry friends, but also for her human friends. She actively participates in class discussions and listens intently while others are speaking. She's great at writing, and at communicating in general. She enjoys classical and folk music, and her pets do too!<br><br>Check out Desiree's gorgeous home and you may get ideas about decorating your own place. She's very friendly and loves having people over. Thanks for being a good citizen, Desiree, and congratulations on being named Citizen of the Week!</div>
